</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At the end of December 2020, Naked Bra=
nd Group Ltd. was a public company (ticker NAKD) with a $45 million market =
capitalization. As its name does not quite suggest, it was <a href=3D"https=
://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25638771.285655/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2=
